&lt;p&gt;At &lt;a href=&#34;http://epic.io&#34;&gt;Epic&lt;/a&gt; we&amp;rsquo;re introducing Epicredits as a currency to help you reward and accomplish what matters to you. You can &lt;a href=&#34;http://makeitepic.com/r/av9iWUHOTP%20&#34;&gt;signup now&lt;/a&gt; to start collecting and get notified when it&amp;rsquo;s live later this year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For those who want to learn more, read on&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://epic.io&#34;&gt;Epic&lt;/a&gt; is based on the realization that more and more of what we do produces a signal in the cloud. Whether it&amp;rsquo;s a tweet, a document update, a blog post or a bookmark there&amp;rsquo;s a record of it somewhere. In fact, when someone is trying to get your attention, even if it&amp;rsquo;s a simple as clicking a link, it&amp;rsquo;s a share of your activity that they want.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
